hority to uproot lawlessness and establish God’s righteousness\n\n- Sunday\n|\nI cook croquetas, and I eat jamon. I keep my diet 100% Mediterranean and drink my Rioja. In that sense, I have a piece of Spain in West Hollywood.\n\n- Paz\n|\nLife is about choosing, experiencing, learning, and choosing again.\n\n- Melissa Heisler, From Type A to Type Me: How to Stop 'Doing' Life and Start Living It\n|\nManaging change is no longer a one-time initiative, and change management turns to be a strategical ongoing capability in today’s digital organizations.\n\n- Pearl Zhu, Digital Capability: Building Lego Like Capability Into Business Competency\n|\nWhat if you were always stuck in one place, your mind spinning and unable to go forward like tires clenched in mud, because the answers wouldn't reveal themselves to you?\n\n- Will Lavender, Obedience\n|\nWhen everyone goes home, you're stuck with yourself.\n\n- Layne\n|\nOriginality is the most deadly mirage in all of art. You can chase it from now until doomsday, and you'll only find yourself lost and dying of thirst.\n\n- Caitlín\n|\nI'm a Gemini, so I change my mind every day.\n\n- Natalie\n|\nI had no desire to hear another woman tell my boyfriend how hot he was. If I wanted him to know, I'd damn well tell him myself.\n\n- Rachel Vincent, Rogue\n|\nPower corrupts, and absolute power corrupts absolutely\n\n- John\n|\nAnd by knowing what we fear, don't we know what we care about, how we are measuring our worth, what success looks like?' I asked. So isn't fear helpful, then?\n\n- Patti\n|\nYou’ve gotta love yourself enough to look INSIDE you & not BESIDE you for your joy, confidence, & self worth.\n\n- Mandy Hale, The Single Woman: Life, Love, and a Dash of Sass\n|\nUnlike a variety of other relationships,friendship requires an acknowledgement by both parties that they are involved or it fails to exist.\n\n- Andrew\n|\nIt is the confession, not the Priest, that gives us absolution\n\n- Christine Iliadis, Paradox of Freedom\n|\